---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import PageHero from "../components/PageHero.astro";
import { business } from "../data/site";
---
<Base
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Angel Plumbing Services Ltd collects, uses and protects your personal data, in line with UK GDPR and the Data Protection Act 2018."
  path="/privacy-policy"
>
  <PageHero eyebrow="Legal" title="Privacy Policy"
    crumbs={[{ label: "Home", href: "/" }, { label: "Privacy Policy", href: "/privacy-policy" }]} />

  <section class="bg-cream">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[80rem] px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-20">
      <div class="prose-legal">
        <p>This Privacy Policy explains how {business.legalName} ("we", "us", "our") collects and uses
          your personal data when you contact us or use this website. We are committed to protecting your
          privacy and handling your data in line with the UK GDPR and the Data Protection Act 2018.</p>

        <h2>Who we are</h2>
        <p>{business.legalName} is the data controller for the personal data you provide. We are a limited
          company registered in England and Wales (company number {business.companyNumber}), with a
          registered office at {business.address.line1}, {business.address.line2}, {business.address.city}
          {business.address.postcode}. You can contact us about your data at
          <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a> or {business.phoneDisplay}.</p>

        <h2>What data we collect</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Information you give us when you complete our enquiry form or contact us - such as your
            name, email address, phone number, property postcode and details of the work you need.</li>
          <li>Information you choose to enter into our on-site tools (for example the period-property tool
            or CP12 reminder tool). Where these tools save your progress, this is stored locally in your
            own browser and is not transmitted to us unless you submit it.</li>
          <li>Limited technical data via optional analytics cookies, only if you accept them (see our
            <a href="/cookie-policy">Cookie Policy</a>).</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>How we use your data, and our lawful basis</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>To respond to your enquiry and provide quotes, site visits and services you request - on the
            basis of taking steps at your request prior to entering a contract, and our legitimate
            interest in running our business.</li>
          <li>To carry out and document work, including statutory gas safety records - to comply with our
            legal obligations.</li>
          <li>To send a CP12 renewal reminder, only where you have asked us to - on the basis of your
            consent, which you can withdraw at any time.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Who we share it with</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your data. We use a third-party form provider to deliver enquiries submitted
          through this website to our inbox, and may use reputable service providers (such as hosting and
          email providers) who process data on our behalf under appropriate safeguards. We may disclose
          data where required by law.</p>

        <h2>How long we keep it</h2>
        <p>We keep enquiry and customer data only for as long as necessary to provide our services and to
          meet our legal, accounting and regulatory obligations, after which it is securely deleted.</p>

        <h2>Your rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to access your personal data, to have it corrected or erased, to restrict or
          object to its processing, and to data portability, in the circumstances set out in the UK GDPR.
          To exercise any of these rights, contact us at <a href={`mailto:${business.email}`}>{business.email}</a>.</p>

        <h2>Complaints</h2>
        <p>If you have a concern about how we handle your data, please contact us first. You also have the
          right to complain to the Information Commissioner's Office (ICO) at
          <a href="https://ico.org.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">ico.org.uk</a>.</p>

        <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
